Texture.name: Color Coded Shulker Box GUI Resource Pack
Texture.role: If you are someone who likes colorful things, I have a new pack for you! Introducing the Color Coded Shulker Box GUI Resource Pack! This pack allows you to change the color of the shulker box GUI to match the color of the shulker box rather than using the default gray color. This resource pack was also designed with compatibility in mind, so it is compatible with many popular UI resource packs.

Texture.name: [Remake/Concept] VDX: Old Days UI - Mid Alpha
Texture.role: An UI Pack (Mid Alpha Version) that brings back some old pocket/desktop UI designs from 2015 (Alpha 0.11.0-0.14-0) for current version of Minecraft Bedrock (Before MC PE/Win10E)! Some UI screens will be styled, others will be 75% accurate about previous UI design.

Texture.name: Animated RGB XP Bar + Classic Inventory GUI
Texture.role: IMPORTANT: Read carefully before download and use! At the moment it is only modified for Classic UI, I still have no plans to do it for Pocket UI. Description : A UI pack to make an animated RGB (Or Chroma) XP bar and level number! But, there's more! ;D And no, it's not affiliated by Razer or Corsair. RGB XP Bar features: Animated RGB XP Bar and Number with total of 40 frames (Very smooth)! For now it is not compatible with external HD textures. But I have added subpack to select appearance between 16x and 32x bar texture (Make sure to restart the game to see the effect). ;)
